  "title": "Two round UFOs spotted hovering over Sobradinho I-DF [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/18/two-round-ufos-spotted-hovering-over-sobradinho-i-df-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-uN",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 19th, 1999</strong>. Time: 16h15, Duration: 3 minutes. In Sobradinho I, Distrito Federal, two unidentified flying objects were observed by two people under good visibility conditions. According to the witnesses, the two round UFOs were red and silver, and were stationary during the whole sighting. They took no photographs and reported no traces of condensation from the observed objects.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.544. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Sobradinho, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>MARCH 19th, 1999. Time: 16h15, Duration: 3 minutes. In Sobradinho I, Distrito Federal, two unidentified flying objects were observed by two people under good visibility conditions. According to the witnesses, the two round UFOs were red and silver, and were stationary during the whole sighting. They took no photographs and reported no traces of condensation [&hellip;]</p>\n",
